8:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Andi and Cohere share a solid foundation of core features including Web Search, Citations. On the other hand, Cohere uniquely offers File Upload and Api Access and Multilingual, giving it an edge for users who prioritize these areas. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Andi holds an overall score of 5/10 and an ease of use score of 9/10, while Cohere scores 7/10 overall and 5/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
9:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, both Andi and Cohere offer flexible pricing models. Both platforms offer free plans, which is great for testing before committing. Andi's free tier and Cohere's free tier each have their own limitations, so it is worth evaluating both to see which free offering better matches your initial needs."}]]}]
